quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  54,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  54,1,qtarabatis Saa'atu wsan shaqqal qamar
  54,2,Wa iny yaraw aayatany yu'ridoo wa yaqooloo sihrum mustamirr
  54,3,Wa kazzaboo wattaba'ooo ahwaaa'ahum; wa kullu amrim mustaqirr
  54,4,Wa laqad jaaa'ahum minal ambaaa'i maa feehi muzdajar
  54,5,Hikmatum baalighatun famaa tughnin nuzur
  54,6,Fatawalla 'anhum; yawma yad'ud daa'i ilaa shai 'in nukur
  54,7,khushsha'an absaaruhum yakrujoona minal ajdaasi ka annahum jaraadum muntashir
  54,8,Muhti'eena ilad daa'i yaqoolul kafiroona haazaa yawmun 'asir
  54,9,Kazzabat qablahum qawmu Noohin fakazzaboo 'abdanaa wa qaaloo majnoo nunw wazdujir
  54,10,Fada'aa Rabbahooo annee maghloobun fantasir
  54,11,Fafatahnaaa abwaabas sa maaa'i bimaa'im munhamir
  54,12,Wa fajjamal arda 'uyoonan faltaqal maaa'u 'alaaa amrin qad qudir
  54,13,Wa hamalnaahu 'alaa zaati alwaahinw wa dusur
  54,14,Tajree bi a'yuninaa jazaaa 'al liman kaana kufir
  54,15,Wa laqat taraknaahaad aayatan fahal mim muddakir
  54,16,Fakaifa kaana 'azaabee wa nuzur
  54,17,Wa laqad yassamal Quraana liz zikri fahal mimmuddakir
  54,18,Kazzabat 'Aadun fakaifa kaana 'azaabee wa nuzur
  54,19,Innaa arsalnaa 'alaihim reehan sarsaran fee Yawmi nahsim mustamirr
  54,20,Tanzi;un naasa ka anna huma'jaazu nakhlim munqa'ir
  54,21,'Fakaifa kaana 'azaabee wa nuzur
  54,22,Wa laqad yassamal Quraana liz zikri fahal mim muddakir
  54,23,Kazzabat Samoodu binnuzur
  54,24,Faqaalooo a-basharam minnaa waahidan nattabi'uhooo innaa izal lafee dalaalinw wa su'ur
  54,25,'A-ulqiyaz zikru 'alaihi mim baininaa bal huwa kazzaabun ashir
  54,26,Sa-ya'lamoona ghadam manil kazzaabul ashir
  54,27,Innaa mursilun naaqati fitnatal lahum fartaqibhum wastabir
  54,28,Wa nabbi'hum annal maaa'a qismatum bainahum kullu shirbim muhtadar
  54,29,Fanaadaw saahibahum fata'aataa fa'aqar
  54,30,Fakaifa kaana 'azaabee wa nuzur
  54,31,Innaaa arsalnaa 'alaihim saihatanw waahidatan fakaano kahasheemil muhtazir
  54,32,Wa laqad yassarnal quraana liz zikri fahal mim muddakir
  54,33,Kazzabat qawmu lootim binnuzur
  54,34,Innaa arsalnaa 'alaihim haasiban illaaa aala Loot najjainaahum bisahar
  54,35,Ni'matam min 'indinaa; kazaalika najzee man shakar
  54,36,Wa laqad anzarahum batshatanaa fatamaaraw binnuzur
  54,37,Wa laqad raawadoohu 'andaifee fatamasnaaa a'yunahum fazooqoo 'azaabee wa nuzur
  54,38,Wa laqad sabbahahum bukratan 'azaabum mustaqirr
  54,39,Fazooqoo 'azaabee wa nuzur
  54,40,Wa laqad yassarnal Quraana liz zikri fahal mim muddakir
  54,41,Wa laqad jaaa'a Aala Fir'awnan nuzur
  54,42,Kazzaboo bi Aayaatinaa kullihaa fa akhaznaahum akhza 'azeezim muqtadir
  54,43,Akuffaarukum khairum min ulaaa'ikum am lakum baraaa'atun fiz Zubur
  54,44,Am yaqooloona nahnu jamee'um muntasir
  54,45,Sa yuhzamul jam'u wa yuwalloonad dubur
  54,46,Balis Saa'atu maw'iduhum was Saa'atu adhaa wa amarr
  54,47,Innal mujrimeena fee dalaalinw wa su'ur
  54,48,Yawma yushaboona fin Naari'alaa wujoohimim zooqoo massa saqar
  54,49,Innaa kulla shai'in khalaqnaahu biqadar
  54,50,Wa maaa amrunaaa illaa waahidatun kalamhim bilbasar
  54,51,Wa laqad ahlaknaaa ashyaa'akum fahal mim muddakir
  54,52,Wa kullu shai'in fa'aloohu fiz Zubur
  54,53,Wa kullu sagheerinw wa kabeerim mustatar
  54,54,Innal muttaqeena fee jannaatinw wa nahar
  54,55,Fee maq'adi sidqin 'inda Maleekim Muqtadir
